Citation.sTitle: Measurement of Activity Coefficients of Solutes at Infinite Dilution in (Dimethyl Sulfoxide + Acetamide, or Formamide, or Urea) Using Gas Liquid Chromatography at the Temperature 298.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: Using gas liquid chromatography, activity coefficients of 12 solutes at infinite dilution in the stationary solvent dimethyl sulfoxide + additives (acetamide, or formamide, or urea) at the temperature 298.15 K have been measured. The effect of composition of the mixed solvents on the activity coefficients at infinite dilution and on selectivity has been discussed.
